title: hg commit "misc/cgo/test: skip test8694 on ARM." does not seem to be in the git repo
body:
The following commit was made after the move to github; I don't see it in the github commit history, so I assume it did not make the migration:

https://code.google.com/p/go/source/detail?r=586738173884643d0dca3fd844f73294984d0b9c

I do not know about other lost commits in the subrepos or in any branches (I only followed https://code.google.com/p/go/source/list).
